OL,3,CCouple distraught after dog 'hit and
OL,4,Ckilled' by e-bike rider who 'laughed'
OL,6,FA couple from Hampshire say they've
OL,7,Fbeen left devastated after their dog
OL,8,Fwas killed in a collision with an
OL,9,Felectric bike.
OL,11,FLee Whitecross was walking his
OL,12,FPomeranian, Saffi, in Sarisbury Green
OL,13,Fone night in February when he says a
OL,14,Fteenager swerved into his pet.
OL,16,FPolice have launched an investigation
OL,17,Fto find the rider who is described as
OL,18,Fbeing between 14 and 18-years-old,
OL,19,Fwhite, and of slim build.
