OL,3,CCouple distraught after dog 'hit and
OL,4,Ckilled' by e-bike rider who 'laughed'
OL,6,FLee and his wife, Julie, are speaking
OL,7,Fout in the hope they can stop this
OL,8,Ffrom happening to anyone else.
OL,10,FLee said: "I see this bike coming
OL,11,Fdown, at a distance. I could hear the
OL,12,Fsound of the bike, the electric sound
OL,13,Fof the bike.
OL,15,F"The next minute, I heard my dog make
OL,16,Fa yelp, I looked down at her, she's
OL,17,Flying on the floor, so I went to pick
OL,18,Fher up.
OL,20,F"She took one look at me and that was
OL,21,Fthe end of her."
