OL,3,CCouple distraught after dog 'hit and
OL,4,Ckilled' by e-bike rider who 'laughed'
OL,6,FJulie said: "There was a frantic
OL,7,Fbanging on the front door, so I went
OL,8,Fdownstairs and there he was, 'Saffi's
OL,9,Fdead, Saffi's dead', absolutely
OL,10,Ffrantic, it just feels like an
OL,11,Fabsolute nightmare."
OL,13,FThe couple had Saffi for 14 years.
OL,14,FThey believe her death wasn't an
OL,15,Faccident.
OL,17,FLee said: "I yelled at the biker, I
OL,18,Fsaid to him, you killed my dog, you
OL,19,Fkilled my dog.
