OL,3,CCouple distraught after dog 'hit and
OL,4,Ckilled' by e-bike rider who 'laughed'
OL,6,F"He looked at me, put the hoodie up
OL,7,Fand laughed.
OL,9,F"For this to happen, for somebody to
OL,10,Fcallously take her life this way and
OL,11,Fride off, it was just devastating."
OL,13,FHampshire Police say they have
OL,14,Flaunched an investigation to find the
OL,15,Frider and they're asking for anyone
OL,16,Fwho might have seen what happened to
OL,17,Fget in touch.
