OL,3,CCouple distraught after dog 'hit and
OL,4,Ckilled' by e-bike rider who 'laughed'
OL,6,FJulie said: "I cry when I'm on my own,
OL,7,Fthat's when I do my crying. I think
OL,8,FI've just kept myself so busy to
OL,9,Fcampaign for better lighting, cameras.
OL,11,F"I've just literally tried to do the
OL,12,Fbest I can for her to find who this
OL,13,Fperson is."
OL,15,FLee added: "I'm just lost without her,
OL,16,FI could get another dog but no other
OL,17,Fdog could ever replace Saffi, she was
OL,18,Fnot just a dog, she was my daughter."
